---
title: Mexican-Style Beyond Meat® and Black Bean Stew with Lime Crema and Zesty Tortilla Chips
description: Perfect for bringing a little heat to your weeknight dinner, this stew is packed with smoky, spicy goodness. Scoop it all up with the zesty tortilla chips to make sure no stew gets left behind!
